description:
Women's ordination is only a SMOKE SCREEN for Satan's 3 step plan to destroy God's Remnant Church, the Seventh-day Adventist Church.
"Woe unto them that call evil good, and good evil...Which justify the wicked for reward, and take away the righteousness of the righteous from him!" Isaiah 5:20,23.
"The very beginning of the great apostasy was in seeking to supplement the authority of God by that of the church. Rome began by enjoining what God had not forbidden, and she ended by forbidding what He had explicitly enjoined.  {GC 289.2}
"Her priests have violated my law, and have profaned mine holy things: they put no difference between the holy and profane, neither have they shewed difference between the unclean and the clean, and have hid their eyes from my Sabbaths, and I am profaned among them." Ezekiel 22:26
